      "content": "i feel like i'm just running in circles. every time i think i finally got my head above water, something just drags me back down. another job lost, another person leaving, another day where i can't even get out of bed. it's like a glitch in my life that just keeps repeating. i'm just so tired of trying to fix something that's fundamentally broken.",
